short_summary: Floating docks repair at Matane fishing harbour in the Gaspesia Peninsula
description: The floating docks repair at Matane fishing harbour in the Gaspesia Peninsula includes, but is not limited to, clearing snow and ice from the 16 floating docks stored in the harbour. Duration of contract: The services of the Contractor shall begin after contract award. The expected completion date of this project is April 30th, 2023.
duration_in_months: You selected the start date of the contract after the notification of contract award.
